533
00:38:47,659 --> 00:38:49,494
<i>uma desculpa incrível.</i>

534
00:38:49,911 --> 00:38:51,496
<i>Uma que os fará parar,</i>

535
00:38:52,247 --> 00:38:53,081
<i>sentar...</i>

536
00:38:53,623 --> 00:38:54,666
<i>e escutar.</i>

537
00:38:56,543 --> 00:38:59,379
<i>Eu estive dentro do Artefato.</i>

538
00:39:00,421 --> 00:39:02,799
